{"tid":1341412,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"光復元朗有必要進行!!!","createTime":"2019-07-21T16:41:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T17:02:15.000Z","uid":92204,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c6de23134ebc9f1fa9cb482eeee7156e41019175","tid":1341412,"uid":92204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:41:36.000Z","msg":"根據今次所謂保衛元朗行動, 我地有百分百必要進行光復元朗行動嚟制裁依班仆制鄉民<br />\n咁樣嘅行動就係佢地所謂嘅保衛家園保衛元朗? 自己街坊都打, 真係人唔笑狗都吠<br />\n我地要問責所謂用心保護市民嘅黑警究竟做咗啲咩! 問下點解依班友點解可以無法無天<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/407353793207073/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fvideos%2F407353793207073%2F&d=YI7gf4cr217w6pzPHhIkRQpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=62df0006\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/407353793207073/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/peterlam020144/videos/10214467005445949/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpeterlam020144%2Fvideos%2F10214467005445949%2F&d=YI7gf4cr217w6pzPHhIkRQpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=0ac0e4f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/peterlam020144/videos/10214467005445949/</a><br />\n班人渣打咗咁耐黑警都唔嚟, 暴徒一散水唔夠幾分鐘就即刻到達現場, 但係仲要慢條斯理慢慢行<br />\n嚟到之後只係同受傷嘅市民爭論, 完全沒有意慾去捉暴從<br />\n涼完冷氣, 引發民憤之後就返去落閘閂門<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kt1kXZJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKt1kXZJ.jpg&h=28e9d6b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n落閘乜都唔洗做, 咁樣就做完你地嘅工作<br />\n我地香港人仲可以去支持依班警察?<br />\n藍絲們盲撐完未? 肯去處理依班真正亂港嘅政權同垃圾自私撚鄉紳啊伯未?<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人! WE ARE AVENGER! NOT PREVENGERS!</span></span>"},{"pid":"1a311198dfdde193d6afa729284e3b9f10a03943","tid":1341412,"uid":70650,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:41:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"347523e488f01ad4709b357e86474d186ed